vi) mininet-wifi> sh ovs-ofctl del-flows s1

vii) Para conseguirmos criar tal parâmetro mudou-se o endereço mac.
mininet-wifi> sh ovs-ofctl add-flow -OOpenFlow13 s1 "dl_type=0x0800, nw_dst=10.10.10.2, actions=mod_dl_dst:1a:4c:07:f4:15:a4"
mininet-wifi> h1 ping -c1 h2
PING 10.0.0.2 (10.0.0.2) 56(84) bytes of data.
From 10.0.0.1 icmp_seq=1 Destination Host Unreachable

--- 10.0.0.2 ping statistics ---
1 packets transmitted, 0 received, +1 errors, 100% packet loss, time 0ms

viii) mininet-wifi> exit
